{"tid":608259,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"稱「觀眾普遍對植入式廣告不反感」　通訊局就放寬規定諮詢公眾","createTime":"2018-03-28T03:52:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T07:06:36.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1c21c22aab9c10936f60ca9866f9b83a19b5b7c6","tid":608259,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T03:52:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180327/s00001/218cd096e840a046efd202c36b032687.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180327%2Fs00001%2F218cd096e840a046efd202c36b032687.jpg&h=8ea2b70e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n通訊事務管理局去年9月公布公眾對植入式廣告意見，逾40%人接受植入式廣告，逾10%人不接受。通訊局認為，觀眾普遍對植入式廣告不反感，決定檢討相關條文。局方早前已完成諮詢廣播業界，將於星期三（28日）諮詢公眾。<br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局表示，通訊局由28日起，就放寬現行規管間接宣傳，和植入式廣告建議諮詢公眾，放寬建議務求在「保障行業發展」和「觀眾利益」之間取得平衡。局長邱騰華說，希望更新規管，能夠給予業內機構更多彈性，對整個廣播業界都有好處。<br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局常任秘書長（通訊及創意產業）利敏貞，上月20日在修訂《廣播條例》及《電訊條例》第一階段公眾諮詢記者會中表示，料今年年中可以處理植入式廣告規管的修訂。<br />\n<br />\n有關植入式廣告爭議，緣自無綫電視2016及2017年，分別就兩個通訊局裁決提出司法覆核。其中包括在2015年12月13日晚舉行《萬千星輝頒獎典禮》中，無綫安排藝人在節目上吃炸雞，裁定嚴重違反守則，被判罰款15萬元。另外無綫2016年4月19日及5月18日兩集《東張西望》內，被通訊局指違規宣傳「myTV SUPER」發警告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180327/s00001/1522163653568\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180327%2Fs00001%2F1522163653568&d=widQjuZiYDQ1igVkOBXowDACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=40e65352\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180327%2Fs00001%2F1522163653568&h=815f05a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180327/s00001/1522163653568</a>"},{"pid":"78746562a3b1d6a6edac9c907f278baedf08ade6","tid":608259,"uid":174084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T03:55:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  無人會再睇電視"},{"pid":"073a2bf98f9b1ac225f7ebe315c8bd8d41fe5bda","tid":608259,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T04:36:57.000Z","msg":"好反感"},{"pid":"d76cfd597bf20b79f1d60e3234eabffdd55b14d1","tid":608259,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T04:44:02.000Z","msg":"留名睇清高撚話仲睇無線"},{"pid":"a99b6abd3219809d463c84fe1c082a63d6e7f637","tid":608259,"uid":51288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d76cfd597bf20b79f1d60e3234eabffdd55b14d1","tid":608259,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T04:44:02.000Z","msg":"留名睇清高撚話仲睇無線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T05:05:50.000Z","msg":"其實而家真係好少睇電視嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7884edc33b10d4629597a8be1fda22f4aaf7aa2e","tid":608259,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T05:10:08.000Z","msg":"免費電視廣播=只播廣告，或偽裝成資訊節目嘅廣告 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37540c4f5e19dfacde0fdef6cb4a133203aa8c6d","tid":608259,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T05:59:50.000Z","msg":"我好撚反感"},{"pid":"b7197b40867f1b984623c2062dc10914866f81f1","tid":608259,"uid":17765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T06:01:49.000Z","msg":"但觀眾普遍對電視廣播有限公司反感嘛<br />\n再植入廣告搵撚到錢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b8e272b6c2e99e77d8d07df9c8730ce2d73c28","tid":608259,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7884edc33b10d4629597a8be1fda22f4aaf7aa2e","tid":608259,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T05:10:08.000Z","msg":"免費電視廣播=只播廣告，或偽裝成資訊節目嘅廣告 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T06:03:28.0